cova.data.taints

Class SymbolicTaint

  • java.lang.Object
    • cova.data.taints.AbstractTaint
      • cova.data.taints.SymbolicTaint
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ImpreciseTaint, SourceTaint

    public abstract class SymbolicTaint
extends AbstractTaint
    The Class SymbolicTaint is an abstract Class of all symbolic taints whose values are uncertain.

    Symbolic taints use symbolicName to represent values. Different than ConcreteTaint whose value can be derived from the program, statically we can not know the value of a SymbolicTaint. SourceTaint and ImpreciseTaint are both symbolic taints.
